CPANPLUS-Shell-Wx version 0.01
==============================

CPANPLUS::Shell::Wx (hereafter known as wxCPAN) is a GUI shell for CPANPLUS.
It has many of the same features as http://search.cpan.org.
To invoke wxCPAN, call `perl -MCPANPLUS -eshell(Wx)` from the command-line.
The program includes full help under the Help menu.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    CPANPLUS
    Cwd
    IPC::Cmd
    Data::Dumper
    Wx
    Module::Load
    Params::Check
    Module::Load::Conditional
    Locale::Maketext::Simple
    File::Spec
    File::HomeDir
    Class::Struct


